node.detail_zh: 患者為 過往健康良好。2 月 20 至 6 月 30 日與母親 ( 第 #1504 宗個案患者) 、胞姊及胞弟 ( 第 #1505 及 #1502 宗個案患者) 曾到印度，抵港後接受強制檢疫，由檢疫中心送院，沒有病徵。
node.detail_en: The patient has good past health. She was in India between February 20 and July 30 with his mother (patient #1504), elder sister, and younger brother (patients #1505 and #1502). Under compulsory quarantine upon arrival in Hong Kong, she was hospitalised from quarantine centre, having exhibited no symptoms.
